25
[p 
	"On this page, I want to document occurences or glitches that haven't been seen before and that are unexplained and not reproducible yet. On this page I also want to provide a guide on how you can provide the best information possible, should such a glitch happen to you. Because recently, people have been unable - or even stubborn - to provide information, leading people to believe their reports might be faked.
	$LF
]p
