[p 
	[b 
		"Notes:
	]b
	" 
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"The player reset his console and mashed the Start key. The game then played the pause sound on the title screen (which is normally not possible) while also starting level 1-1. The game was then muted. The player proceeded to finish the level and softlocked until he paused and unpaused the game which brought the sound back.
	$LF
]p
